<h2>Your shared account and related services</h2><p>If you create an account on ScienceDirect, Scopus, Mendeley, ClinicalKey or any of the other Elsevier services listed <a href="https://service.elsevier.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/14372">here</a>, you can sign in with the same credentials to all of them.</p>&nbsp;<a class="toggle-hidden-content" href="#" title="call-to-action">Read more</a>
</div>
<div class="matrix-show-hide-content" style="display: none; padding-top:15px"><p>We will share your usage activity, preferences and other information amongst these and related Elsevier services to help you improve your productivity. For example, ScienceDirect may recommend better content for you based on your Mendeley library content and the abstracts you read on Scopus, and Mendeley could present you a better tailored content feed based on your ScienceDirect and Scopus activity.</p></div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row row-tight">
    <div class="large-12 columns">
    <h2>Your choices and communications preferences</h2><p>You can manage your communications preferences and interests when you register with the Service, by updating your account preferences, by using the &ldquo;opt-out&rdquo; or unsubscribe mechanism or other means provided within the communications that you receive from us or by contacting us. We reserve the right to notify you of changes or updates to the Service whenever necessary.</p>
    </div>
</div><div class="large-12 columns" id="content_container_150407_150407">
<div class="row row-tight">
<div class="large-12 columns" id="" style="padding-bottom:15px">
